Class oracle.html.PasswordField

public class PasswordField
extends Item
Description:

A PasswordField is the same as a text field element, except that the value is obscured as it is entered

Instructions:

Use this class to present user with a text entry field for password entry purposes.

Example: 

// Create a PasswordField Object
PasswordField passwd = new PasswordField("passwd");

See Also:
TextField, Item
